{
  "chapter": 21,
  "chapter_summary": "第二十一回\"以友为荣\"。伊哭与林仙儿事后来到客栈，伊哭问起阿飞，林仙儿故意挑拨，激伊哭去杀阿飞。伊哭深夜突袭阿飞房间，两人在窗外空隙对峙。伊哭以青魔手压制阿飞，断其长剑，阿飞佯装求饶，趁伊哭出手稍慢之际，以断剑尖刺入其咽喉，一击毙命。阿飞冷然道：\"谁侮辱她，谁就得死。\"次日清晨，林仙儿见阿飞在窗外守候，以温柔姿态迷惑阿飞，阿飞对她愈发痴迷。二人前往饭厅，遇说书人孙老先生携孙女红儿在客栈说书。孙老先生讲述梅花盗与李探花的故事，揭露李寻欢被诬为梅花盗、护送心眉大师回少林、却反遭少林弟子围困于禅房的经过。阿飞听闻李寻欢身陷少林八百弟子包围之中，热血沸腾，深感以有李寻欢这样的朋友为荣。故事以孙老先生的叹息结尾——除非有人能证明李寻欢不是梅花盗，否则少林弟子绝不会放他走。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "现在你总该知道我是不是值得的了吧？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我真该杀了你的，否则还不知有多少人要死在你手上。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "你本是来杀我的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 14,
      "line_end": 14
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "你下得了手？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "跟你一起来的那小伙子是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "你为什么要问他？是吃醋，还是害怕？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "他是个乖孩子，不像你这么坏，早就远远找了间屋子去睡觉了，他若在附近能听到声音的地方，怎会让你如此欺负我？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "他听不到，是他的运气。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "哦？你难道还想杀了他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 30,
      "line_end": 30
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "哼。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "你杀不了他的，他的武功很高，而且是李寻欢的朋友，我也很喜欢他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 34,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "他就住在前面那排屋子最后一间，你敢去找他么？",
      "tone": "挑衅",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "小心些呀，你的咽喉上若再挨一剑，那就糟了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你和林仙儿一起来的？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "好，你出来。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我要杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "今天我却不愿杀人，你走吧。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "今天我也不想杀人，只想杀你。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 94,
      "line_end": 94
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 96
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你不该和林仙儿一起来的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "你若再叫她的名字，我只得杀你了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "因为你不配。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我不但要叫她的名字，还要跟她睡觉，你又能怎样！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "这样的武功，也配和我动手，林仙儿还说你武功不错。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你若肯老老实实地回答我两句话，我就饶了你。",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yi_ku",
      "speaker_name": "伊哭",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我问你，林仙儿是不是常常陪人睡觉的，她和你睡过觉没有？",
      "tone": "狞笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "我，我说！",
      "tone": "痛苦",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_yi_ku",
      "text": "谁侮辱她，谁就得死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "外面是小飞吗？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 186
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "是我。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你为何不进来？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你没有闩门？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我忘了……我什么都忘了。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "你……你出了事？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我若没有睡好，脸就会肿的……昨天晚上我一直翻来覆去地睡不着……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 202,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你为什么这样盯着人家看？我就是睡不着嘛，你……你……你又想到什么地方去了？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你呢？你睡得好么？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "我也没有睡好，有条疯狗一直在我窗子外乱叫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "疯狗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "嘿，我已宰了它，将它抛在河里了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你不想去听？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 228
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "不想。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "我倒想去听听，何况，我们总是要吃饭的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "text": "看来这伙计拉生意的法子倒真用对了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "你坏死了……还不快把衣服拿给我。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "转过去，可不准偷看。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "红儿，时候到了么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "是时候了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lin_xian_er",
      "speaker_name": "林仙儿",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "看来这位孙老先生倒不像是跑江湖，骗饭吃的混混。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "梅花盗无恶不作，探花郎仗义疏财。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位可知道我说的这两人是谁么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这两人是谁呀？好像没有听说过。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "那你就真是孤陋寡闻了，提起这两人，当真是大大有名，'梅花盗'数十年，只出现过两次，但两河绿林道中，千千百百条好汉所做的案子，加起来也没有他一个人多。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "好厉害……但那位探花郎又是谁呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "此人乃是位世家公子，历代缨鼎，可说是显赫已极，三代中就中过七次进士，只可惜没中过状元，到了李探花这一代，膝下的两位少爷更是天资绝顶，才气纵横，他老人家将希望全都寄托在这两位公子身上，只望他们能中个状元，来弥补自己的缺陷……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "探花就已经不错了，为何一定要中状元呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "谁知大李公子一考，又是个探花，父子两人都郁郁不欢，只望小李公子能争气，谁知命不由人，这位小李公子虽然惊才绝艳，但一考之下，也是个探花，老探花失望之下，没过两年就去世了，接着，大李探花也得了不治之症，这位小李探花心灰意冷，索性辞去了官职，在家里疏财结客，他的慷慨与豪爽，就算孟尝复生信陵再世，只怕也比不上他。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "这位探花郎不但才高八斗，而且还是位文武全才，幼年就经异人传授了他一身惊世骇俗的绝顶功夫。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "爷爷今天要说的，就是他们两人的故事么？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那一定好听极了，只不过……只不过堂堂的探花郎，又怎会和声名狼藉的梅花盗牵涉到一起了呢？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "这其中自有道理。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "什么道理？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "只因梅花盗就是探花郎，探花郎就是梅花盗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这位李探花既然不惜散尽万金家财，想必是个视金钱如粪土的人，又怎会忽然变成了打家劫舍、贪财好色的梅花盗？我不信。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 327
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "莫说你不信，我也不信，所以特地去打听了很久。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "若论打听消息，谁也没有你老人家拿手，其中的详情，你老人家想必一定打听出来了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "自然打听出来了，这其中的详情，实在是曲折复杂，诡谲离奇，而且紧张刺激，精彩绝伦……",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "你老人家怎么不说了呀？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 338
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "刚说到好听的地方，就不说了，岂非是吊人的胃口？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "我明白了，你老人家原来是想喝酒。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "事情开始，是发生在兴云庄。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "兴云庄？那莫非是龙啸云龙四爷住的地方么？听说那里气象恢宏，宅第连云，庭园林木之胜，更冠于两河，是个好地方。",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 354,
      "line_end": 357
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "不错，但这好地方却本是李寻欢送给他的，只因这两人乃是生死八拜之交，而且龙夫人还是李探花的姑表之亲……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 360,
      "line_end": 360
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "如此说来，梅花盗莫非已死在那位……'飞剑客'手上么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 368,
      "line_end": 370
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "但赵大爷、田七爷，却认为他杀的不是梅花盗，李寻欢才是真的梅花盗。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 372,
      "line_end": 374
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那么究竟谁才是真的梅花盗呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 376,
      "line_end": 376
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "谁也没有见过真的梅花盗，谁也不知道哪个是真，哪个是假。但赵大爷、田大爷身份不同，一言九鼎，他们老说李寻欢是梅花盗，那别人也只好说李寻欢是梅花盗了，于是心眉大师就要将他押回少林寺。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 378,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "谁知到少林寺时，却变成是李探花将心眉大师送回去的了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 384,
      "line_end": 386
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "原来押送他的心眉大师、田七和四位少林弟子都在半路上遭了苗疆极乐峒主的毒手，心眉大师中毒后才释放了李寻欢，李寻欢见他中毒已深，只有少林寺中还可能有解药，是以就将他护送回去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 392,
      "line_end": 394
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这位李探花可真是位大英雄、大豪杰，若是换了别人，在这种情况下早已不愿而去了，怎肯救他？",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 396,
      "line_end": 398
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "话虽不错，只可惜少林僧人们非但不感激他，还要杀他。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 400,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 404,
      "line_end": 404
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "因为这些话都是李探花自己说出来的，少林僧人们对他说的话连一个字都不相信。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 406,
      "line_end": 408
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "可是……可是那心眉大师总该为他证实才是。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 410,
      "line_end": 410
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "只可惜心眉大师一回到少林后，就已圆寂了，除了心眉大师外，世上再也没有第二个人知道这件事的真相！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 412,
      "line_end": 414
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_a_fei",
      "speaker_name": "阿飞",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "那位李探花莫非已遭了少林寺的毒手？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 418,
      "line_end": 420
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_a_fei",
      "text": "少林寺虽然领袖武林，门下弟子更无一不是绝顶高手，但若想杀死李探花，却也非易事。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 422,
      "line_end": 424
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但双拳难对四手，好汉架不住人多，李探花就算天下无敌，又怎能挡得住少林寺的八百弟子？",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 426,
      "line_end": 428
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "少林寺纵有八百弟子，无数好手，却又有谁敢抢先出手？又有谁敢去接小李探花的第一刀？！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 430,
      "line_end": 432
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "不错，小李神刀，例不虚发，少林寺纵有八百弟子，也一定伤不了他的，他现在只怕早已走了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 434,
      "line_end": 436
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "他还没有走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 438,
      "line_end": 438
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 440,
      "line_end": 440
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "少林弟子虽然无法伤他，但他也无法杀出少林弟子的包围，此刻是非未明，真相未白，他也不能走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 442,
      "line_end": 444
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "他既不能走，也不能打，那怎么办呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 446,
      "line_end": 446
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "他身在八百弟子的包围之中，飞刀若一出手，就必死无疑，只因少林弟子怕的就是他手中之刀，而他的飞刀再强，却也杀不尽八百弟子。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 448,
      "line_end": 450
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但这样耗下去也不行呀！一个人总有支持不住的时候。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 452,
      "line_end": 454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "当时他们说话之处就在心眉大师圆寂的禅房外，双方说僵了，李探花就乘机冲入了那禅房中。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 458,
      "line_end": 460
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这么一来，他岂非自己将自己困死了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 462,
      "line_end": 462
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "少林弟子正也因为未想到他不向外面冲，反而自人绝路，所以才会被他冲人禅房去，后悔已来不及了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 464,
      "line_end": 466
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "后悔？李寻欢既已自入绝路，他们为何还要后悔？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 468,
      "line_end": 468
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "禅房中不但有心眉大师的遗蜕，还有一部少林寺内珍藏的经典，他们投鼠忌器，更不敢冲进去动手了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 470,
      "line_end": 471
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "但他们老在外面将这禅房围住，用不了几天，小李探花岂非就要被饿死，渴死了！",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 474,
      "line_end": 476
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "少林弟子想必也是打的这个主意，怎奈他们的五师叔心树还留在那禅房，而且又被李探花制住，他们难道能将他们的五师叔也一齐饿死么？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 478,
      "line_end": 480
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "当然不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 482,
      "line_end": 482
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "所以他们只有将食物和水送进去，心树饿不死，李探花自然也饿不死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 484,
      "line_end": 484
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "少林寺号称武林圣地，数百年来，谁也不敢妄越雷池一步，但李探花单枪匹马一个人，就将少林寺闹得人仰马翻，少林八百弟子非但拿他无可奈何，还得每天请他吃喝，还生怕送去的东西不中他的意……",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 488,
      "line_end": 488
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "这位李探花可真是位了不起的人物，这故事真好听极了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 490,
      "line_end": 491
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "不错，李探花的确是位了不起的英雄豪杰，可惜这位大英雄迟早还是免不了要埋骨少林寺的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 498,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
      "listener": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 502,
      "line_end": 502
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_sun_lao_xian_sheng",
      "speaker_name": "孙老先生",
      "listener": "char_hong_er",
      "text": "除非有人能证明李寻欢不是梅花盗，能证明心眉大师的确是被五毒童子所害，否则少林弟子就绝不会放他走！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 21,
      "line_start": 504,
      "line_end": 506
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_er",
      "speaker_name": "红儿",
